  <brief_title>VEGA System® Study in the Total Knee Arthroplasty</brief_title>
  <official_title>Prospective Non-interventional, Prospective Multicenter Study of VEGA System® Prosthesis in the Total Knee Arthroplasty</official_title>
  <sponsors>
