  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This post-market clinical follow-up study intends to investigate long-term functionality of
      the VEGA System®. The design of the VEGA System® is meant to provide the patient with more
      knee mobility compared to their pre-operative state.The endpoint is the revision of at least
      one of the prosthesis components
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
