  <primary_outcome>
    <measure>Survival rate of the prosthesis at 5 years</measure>
    <time_frame>needs of revision of at least one of the prosthesis component evaluated 5 years after the knee arthroplasty</time_frame>
    <description>If a patient withdraws from the study for any reason, counts as the end date for the survival of the implant of the last day on which the implants were well known even in place</description>
  </primary_outcome>
